data.description:
A beautiful country home nestled on 3.35 acres in Lincoln County, Mississippi. This home is situated on a small, quiet one lane street with woods all around. This home is engulfed with privacy while retaining convenience, as it sits less than 6 miles to all the local shopping and less than 4 miles to I-55.
It is a perfect home for those who require not only a large indoor space, but an equally large outdoor space.  The yard is beautifully landscaped and well-maintained with a rocking chair front porch. The house has a large back porch off the kitchen, which could easily be converted to an indoor sun room or a screened in back porch. A large outdoor area with a flagstone patio and a covered grilling space. There is 500 square foot open multi-use family room, which has a 400 square foot walk in attic above it. There is a 900 square foot shop (30'x30') which houses a 500 square foot gym.
There is a large deck off of the back porch that needs repairs.
